Interface PlayerMovementListener


  • public interface PlayerMovementListener
    A PlayerMovementListener is notified before and after the player moves rooms

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean playerMove(Room from, Room to, boolean beforeMove)
      Called when a player moves rooms.

    • Method Detail

      • playerMove

        boolean playerMove(Room from,
                 Room to,
                 boolean beforeMove)
        Called when a player moves rooms.
        Parameters:
        from - the room the player is moving, or has moved, from
        to - the room the player is moving, or has moved, to
        beforeMove - true if this method is being called before the player moves
        Returns:
        true if the further processing of the player move command should be blocked; false to let processing continue as usual.
        See Also:
        GameManager.addBeforePlayerMovementListener(PlayerMovementListener), GameManager.addAfterPlayerMovementListener(PlayerMovementListener)
